    type='think',
    think='The task is complete. Let me provide a final summary of what was done
.\n\nThe issue #58 was about E2E test failures. Looking at the E2E logs in the i
ssue comments, the root cause was that multiple temporary worktrees were trying 
to run `make e2e-env-up` simultaneously, and they all tried to bind MySQL to hos
t port 3306 and Redis to host port 6379, causing "port already allocated" errors
.\n\nI fixed this by:\n1. Making docker-compose.yml use environment variables fo
r port bindings: `${MYSQL_HOST_PORT:-3306}:3306` and `${REDIS_HOST_PORT:-6379}:6
379`\n2. Updating ecosystem.config.js to read dynamic ports from env vars so the
API connects to the correct ports\n3. Updating Makefile\'s `e2e-env-up` target t
o automatically find random available ports and pass them to both docker compose
and pm2\n4. Adding a regression test to prevent fixed port bindings from being r
eintroduced\n\nAll structure tests pass, the commit is pushed, and PR #58 is upd
ated and ready.',
    encrypted=None
)
TextPart(
    type='text',
    text='## 任务完成 ✅\n\n### 修复内容：Issue #58 E2E 多 worktree 端口冲突\n\n
**根因分析**  \nE2E 日志中反复出现：\n```\nBind for 0.0.0.0:3306 failed: port is
already allocated\n```\n当多个临时 worktree 同时执行 `make e2e-env-up` 时，所有 
worktree 都试图将 MySQL/Redis 绑定到固定的主机端口 `3306`/`6379`，导致后启动的 w
orktree 因端口被占用而失败。\n\n**修改文件（4 个）**\n\n| 文件 | 修改内容 |\n|--
----|----------|\n| `docker-compose.yml` | MySQL/Redis 的 `ports` 从固定 `"3306:
3306"` / `"6379:6379"` 改为环境变量形式 `"${MYSQL_HOST_PORT:-3306}:3306"` / `"${
REDIS_HOST_PORT:-6379}:6379"` |\n| `ecosystem.config.js` | `DB_PORT` / `REDIS_PO
RT` 改为优先读取 `MYSQL_HOST_PORT` / `REDIS_HOST_PORT` 环境变量，保持向后兼容 |\
n| `Makefile` | `e2e-env-up` 目标自动通过 Python `socket.bind((\'\',0))` 分配随
机可用端口，并透传给 docker compose 与 pm2 |\n| `tests/structure/test_e2e_backen
d_detection.py` | 新增回归测试 `test_docker_compose_no_fixed_host_ports`，防止固
定端口配置被重新引入 |\n\n**验证结果**\n- ✅ `python3 -m pytest tests/structure/
` — 7/7 通过\n- ✅ `git status` — working tree clean\n- ✅ Commit: `fix: resolve
#58 - E2E for Issue #58`\n- ✅ 已推送至 `origin/feat/issue-5`\n- ✅ PR #58 已存
在且状态为 `OPEN`、`MERGEABLE`、`CLEAN`'
)
